          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Cryogenic liquid 4He target in form of cylinder with",
                "length of 20 cm and 4 cm in diameter. The cylindrical",
                "axis of the target cell was aligned along the beam",
                "axis.The liquid 4He was maintained at 3.4 K with a",
                "target thickness of (4.17+-0.04)E+23 nuclei/cm2. The",
                "walls and end windows of the cell were made from",
                "0.125-mm-thick Kapton foil."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The Compton scattered photons were detected",
                "by an array of eight NaI(Tl) detectors with core",
                "diameter of 25.4 cm surrounded by eight annular",
                "segments of 7.5-cm-thick NaI(Tl) crystals. The",
                "lengths of the core NaI crystals ranged from 25.4 to",
                "30.5 cm. The annular segments were used as an",
                "anticoincidence shield to veto the cosmic-ray",
                "background. Detectors were placed at scattering",
                "angles of theta = 55deg, 90deg and 125deg in the",
                "laboratory frame."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "LCS"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The HIgS facility produces a quasimonoenergetic",
                "Compton backscattered photon beam tunable in wide",
                "energy range with either linear or circular",
                "polarization. The gamma-ray beam pulses have a width",
                "of about 300 ps FWHM and are separated by 179 ns."
              ]
            }
          ],
